{"article_id":"duaehapXFq7c9zKR","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President to address Democrats in Congress on how to save signature legislation","depth":10},{"id":1,"text":"while future vice-president will meet with Republicans","depth":11},{"id":2,"text":"eager to repeal the law","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"Barack Obama and vice president-elect Mike Pence will have a showdown on Capitol Hill on Wednesday","depth":13},{"id":4,"text":"as the gloves come off in the fight over US healthcare .","depth":13},{"id":5,"text":"The president will address House and Senate Democrats over how to counter Donald Trump ' s stated objective","depth":14},{"id":6,"text":"of repealing the Affordable Care Act , a cornerstone of his legacy .","depth":14},{"id":7,"text":"Strategies are likely to focus on aspects of Obamacare","depth":15},{"id":8,"text":"that have bipartisan support","depth":15},{"id":9,"text":"as well as exploiting Republican divisions over how to replace it .","depth":14},{"id":10,"text":"Republicans ' plan","depth":13},{"id":11,"text":"to erase Obama legacy","depth":13},{"id":12,"text":"starts with chipping away at Obamacare","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"Read more","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"Pence , meanwhile , will address a meeting with House Republicans","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"and attend a lunch with their Senate counterparts .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"A new , Republican-controlled Congress convened on Tuesday","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"eager to repeal Obamacare","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"after years of opposition .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Wednesday will mark a poignant , high-stakes return to Capitol Hill for Obama ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"who in 2009 delivered a landmark speech to the House for fundamental healthcare reform","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that had eluded presidents for decades .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"In a sign of the bitter wrangling","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"to come ,","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"at one point he was interrupted by Republican Joe Wilson ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"who shouted :","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"\" You lie ! \"","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"The White House claims","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"that ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"despite teething troubles ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"Obamacare has been a singular achievement .","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"It brought health insurance to 22 million people","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"and , for the first time in US history , means","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"that more than 90 % of Americans are insured .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"Press secretary Josh Earnest told reporters on Tuesday :","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"\" I know","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"that particularly at this time","depth":15},{"id":37,"text":"when there ' s a lot of discussion about the president ' s legacy ,","depth":15},{"id":38,"text":"some people might think","depth":15},{"id":39,"text":"well ,","depth":15},{"id":40,"text":"the president ' s very concerned about political capital","depth":15},{"id":41,"text":"that he ' s invested in this","depth":15},{"id":42,"text":"and doesn ' t want to see it all go away . \"","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"That ' s certainly true ,","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"but the president ' s priority and the president ' s motivation is rooted in looking out for the interests of the 22 million Americans","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"whose healthcare would be taken away","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"if Republicans repeal the Affordable Care Act . \"","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"Obama is concerned about a devastating impact on Medicare ,","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"which protects millions of elderly people ,","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"and Medicaid , a programme for low-income Americans ,","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"Earnest added .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"He said :","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"\" It ' s not surprising to me that there are some Republicans","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"who are now a little queasy about the prospect of the impact","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"that repealing Obamacare would have on their own supporters , on people in their own congressional districts ,","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"because we know","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"there are people all across the country","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"who benefit from this law ,","depth":15},{"id":58,"text":"who are protected by this law ,","depth":16},{"id":59,"text":"whose lives have been saved by this law ,","depth":16},{"id":60,"text":"and the prospect","depth":16},{"id":61,"text":"of taking it away","depth":16},{"id":62,"text":"is a question of life or death for some people . \"","depth":15},{"id":63,"text":"Earnest suggested","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"that Obama would encourage Democrats to focus on aspects of the Affordable Care Act","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"that have bipartisan support .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"An obvious example is consumer protection","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"that prevents employer discrimination against people with a pre-existing condition .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"\" They should be out there","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"telling the stories of their constituents","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"who benefit from this law . \"","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"During the election campaign , Trump vowed to immediately repeal and replace Obamacare","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"although ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"after meeting the president ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"he indicated","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"that some parts might be preserved .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"He nevertheless nominated a health secretary , Tom Price ,","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"who is an ardent critic of the law .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"And this week Trump tweeted :","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"\" People must remember","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"that ObamaCare just doesn ' t work ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"and it is not affordable","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"- 116 % increases","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"( Arizona ) .","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"Bill Clinton called it ' CRAZY ' \"","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"He added :","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"\" The Democrat Governor of Minnesota said","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"' The Affordable Care Act","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"( ObamaCare )","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"is no longer affordable ! ' -","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"And , it is lousy healthcare . \"","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"As promised ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Republicans wasted no time","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"getting down to business","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"when the 115th Congress convened on Tuesday .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"Senate budget committee chairman Mike Enzi , a Republican from Wyoming , introduced a resolution","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"that he touted as a \" first step \"","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"toward repealing the president ' s signature healthcare law .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"The resolution includes \" reconciliation instructions \"","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"that would enable Republicans to dismantle key provisions of the law with a simple 51-vote majority in the Senate .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"Using this budgetary maneuver ,","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Republicans can undo enough of the law","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"to render it functionally ineffective .","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"Addressing the Senate for the first time as minority leader ,","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"Chuck Schumer , of New York , said","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"it was \" not acceptable to repeal \" the healthcare law","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"and \" throw our healthcare system into chaos","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"and then leave the hard work for another day \" .","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"What an Obamacare replacement could look like under Tom Price","depth":4},{"id":109,"text":"Read more","depth":3},{"id":110,"text":"In a statement , House speaker Paul Ryan applauded the resolution ,","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"it \" sets the stage for repeal","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"followed by a stable transition to a better healthcare system \" .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"He added :","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"\" Our goal is to ensure","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"that patients will be in control of their healthcare","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"and have greater access to quality , affordable coverage . \"","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"However , unravelling Obamacare ' s provisions ,","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"which offer tax credits","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"for purchasing private health insurance","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"and allow states to expand coverage of Medicaid ,","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"is complicated .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"It may be expedient to replace those provisions with other forms of healthcare coverage ,","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"but House and Senate Republicans are divided on how to go about it .","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"Some Republicans have conceded benefits from Obamacare ,","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"whereas others are fiercely opposed .","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"Representative Steve King of Iowa said :","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"\" I ' m for the complete , 100 % , rip-out-by-the-roots repeal of Obamacare .","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"I don ' t want to leave any vestige of it behind , not one particle of its DNA in law . \"","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"Trump has wavered on his campaign promise","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"to \" repeal and replace \" Obamacare .","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"In a meeting with Obama after his election , Trump indicated","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"that he was open to parts of the law , especially the measures","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"that bar insurance agencies from refusing to cover people with pre-existing conditions","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"and allow young people to stay on their parents ' health insurance","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"until they ' re 26 .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"At Trump ' s New Year ' s Eve bash at his Mar-A-Lago estate in Florida , the president-elect thrilled the crowd","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"when he said :","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"\" We ' re going to get rid of Obamacare . \"","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"A recent study by the Commonwealth Fund ,","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"which was analyzed by the Rand corporation ,","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"found","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"that implementing Trump ' s healthcare proposal would cause nearly 20 million people to lose insurance coverage in 2018 .","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"When people with no insurance are admitted to the hospital ,","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"the costs are often shifted to taxpayers .","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"On Tuesday morning , Kellyanne Conway , a top adviser to Trump , said","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"that the replacement process would be seamless .","depth":7},{"id":148,"text":"Asked if someone","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"currently covered under the healthcare","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"would have healthcare","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"after it ' s repealed ,","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"she replied :","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"\" That is correct . \"","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"\" We don ' t want anyone","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"who currently has insurance","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"to not have insurance , \"","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"Conway said on MSNBC ' s Morning Joe .","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"\" Also we are very aware","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"that the public likes coverage for pre-existing conditions .","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"There are some pieces of merit in the current plan . \"","depth":7},{"id":161,"text":"Democrats are planning to launch an effort","depth":3},{"id":162,"text":"to mobilise grassroots support for Obamacare","depth":3},{"id":163,"text":"by explaining how its repeal would create a ripple effect","depth":3},{"id":164,"text":"hurting a majority of Americans .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":329,"left":325,"right":328,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":325,"left":273,"right":324,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":255,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":255,"left":235,"right":254,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":235,"left":191,"right":234,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":183,"right":190,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":180,"right":182,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":178,"right":179,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":178,"left":167,"right":177,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":167,"left":0,"right":166,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":176,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":173,"right":175,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":168,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":169,"right":171,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":170,"right":9,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":170,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":174,"right":12,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":174,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":182,"left":16,"right":181,"relation":"elaboration","nucleari